#: ../../source/reference/dataframe/generated/maxframe.dataframe.Index.astype.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.dataframe.Index.astype"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.astype.index_astype:1 of
msgid "Create an Index with values cast to dtypes."
msgstr "创建一个值被转换为指定数据类型的 Index。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.astype.index_astype:3 of
msgid ""
"The class of a new Index is determined by dtype. When conversion is "
"impossible, a ValueError exception is raised."
msgstr "新 Index 的类由 dtype 决定。当转换不可行时，将引发 ValueError 异常。"

#: ../../source/reference/dataframe/generated/maxframe.dataframe.Index.astype.rst
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.astype.index_astype:6 of
msgid ""
"Note that any signed integer `dtype` is treated as ``'int64'``, and any "
"unsigned integer `dtype` is treated as ``'uint64'``, regardless of the "
"size."
msgstr ""
"请注意，任何有符号整数 `dtype` 都被视为 ``'int64'``，任何无符号整数 `"
"dtype` 都被视为 ``'uint64'``，无论其大小如何。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.astype.index_astype:10 of
msgid ""
"By default, astype always returns a newly allocated object. If copy is "
"set to False and internal requirements on dtype are satisfied, the "
"original data is used to create a new Index or the original Index is "
"returned."
msgstr ""
"默认情况下，astype 总是返回一个新分配的对象。如果 copy 设置为 False 且 "
"dtype 的内部要求得到满足，则使用原始数据创建新的 Index 或返回原始 Index。"

#: ../../source/reference/dataframe/generated/maxframe.dataframe.Index.astype.rst
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.astype.index_astype:16 of
msgid "Index with values cast to specified dtype."
msgstr "值被转换为指定数据类型的 Index。"

#: ../../source/reference/dataframe/generated/maxframe.dataframe.Index.astype.rst
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

